casebody.data:
Wednesday, October 2, 1991

MERIT DOCKET

91-1137. State, ex rel. Hwang, v. Mahoning Cty.

Court of Common Pleas. In Prohibition. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Wright, J., would overrule the motion to dismiss, allow an answer, and deny the motion for leave to file amicus of Sinkovich.
